hopobject.body: How long are you planning to stay here? arcoxia etoricoxib dose I think most THFC supporters miss the point as usual, you are a selling club Levy just wants to extract top dollar. As for Bale the deal that will set him and family up for life even if he has a career ending injury next year, what is the point of staying at the end of the day it is about money. Get over it and move on go and find the next good player to progress and sell on.
